Insight 10: Transient Guests Drive Volume — Group Guests Are the Most Reliable

Customer Type	Bookings	Share	Cancel Rate	Avg ADR	Avg Lead Time	Avg Nights
Transient	88,272	75.1%	41.34%	$108.56	94.4 days	3.48
Transient-Party	24,702	21.0%	25.85%	$87.55	137.8 days	3.07
